% Form: Intro(1-2) A1(3-6) A2(7-10) B(11-14, bar14=near-silent breath before the climax) C-climax(15-18) Outro/tag(19-20)
% Arc: restless/unsettled urgency (Intro-B, D natural minor/Dorian-ish color) -> triumphant release (C-Outro,
%   parallel D major/Lydian via explicit accidentals; K:Dm key signature is kept the whole piece, no modulation)
% Hook: syncopated pickup into a held target a minor 3rd up (D->F), stated bare in the Intro, complete+ascending
%   in A1, sequenced up a step in A2, transformed into a register-leap major statement at the climax (bar 15)
% Drums are NOT encoded in this ABC file (percussion is unpitched, GM channel 10). See drums.json (step-grid)
%   and song.mid (merged output) -- abc-to-midi-orchestration handles the drum conversion and merge separately.
% Groove: straight (unswung) driving 7/8 feel. groove-profiles.md's only named pocket (neo-soul-core) is
%   laid-back and does not fit this energetic fusion feel, so no %%pocket directive is declared here
%   (see composition-plan.json "interpretive_choices" and quality-report.md).
% --- Melody (lead sheet: melody + chord symbols) ---
[V:Melody] "Dm9"z2 z D F3 | "Dm11"z7 | "Dm9"z2 z D F G A | "Gm7"A3 G F E2 |
[V:Melody] "Dm9"z2 z D F3 | "A7sus4"G4 z3 | "Dm9"z2 z e g3 | "Bbmaj7#11"a2 b2 a3 |
[V:Melody] "Gm7"g2 a2 b3 | "A7b9"b3 c'2 z2 | "Bb7#11"d' c' b _a g f2 | "A7b9"b4 z3 |
[V:Melody] "A7b9"c'2 ^c'2 d'3 | "A7b9"z7 | "Dmaj7#11"z2 z d' ^f'3 | "Dmaj7#11"e'3 d'2 ^c'2 |
[V:Melody] "Gmaj7#11"e'2 d'2 ^c'3 | "Dmaj9"d'4 z3 | "A7sus4"^f'2 e'2 d'3 | "Dmaj7#11"d'7 |]
